title: Bug 116564 - Hyperlink builder title changes with settings
description: The title of the hyperlink builder is not being displayed correctly. It changes from 'Hyperlink Options' to 'www.actuate.com' after clicking on 'OK' and reopening the hyperlink builder.
OB: Clicking on 'OK' and reopening the hyperlink builder results in the title being displayed as 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected behavior is for the title to be displayed as 'Hyperlink Options' in the hyperlink builder.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'. 
2. Click on 'OK' to save the changes. 
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
